        "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/eshad/macscp/zipball/v1.0.0",
        "body": "## MacSCP v1.0.0\n\nA native macOS SCP/SSH file transfer app with dual-pane file browser.\n\n### Features\n- Dual-pane local/remote file browser\n- SSH key and password authentication\n- Keychain storage for saved connection passwords\n- File upload/download via rsync with sudo support\n- Directory transfer support\n- Multi-file drag-and-drop between panels\n- Copy/paste files between local and remote (Cmd+C/V)\n- Inline rename, new folder creation\n- Type-to-select and search/filter files\n- File watcher for auto-uploading edited remote files\n- Path bar with autocomplete\n- Multi-tab connections\n\n### Install\nDownload `MacSCP.dmg`, open it, and drag MacSCP to your Applications folder.",
        "short_description_html": "<h2>MacSCP v1.0.0</h2>\n<p>A native macOS SCP/SSH file transfer app with dual-pane file browser.</p>\n<h3>Features</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Dual-pane local/remote file browser</li>\n<li>SSH key and password authentication</li>\n<li>Keychain storage for saved conn…</li>\n</ul>",
